{
  "texts": [
    "He received a B.Eng.",
    "in Computer Science from Nankai University in 2019.",
    "His research interests focus on generative image editing, as well as tackling distribution shift scenarios in deep learning such as Continual Learning, Federated Learning, etc.",
    "Yongqi Xu is with the School of Computer Science and Technology, Guangdong University of Technology, Guangzhou, China.",
    "He is a master's candidate at the School of Environment and Energy, Peking University (PKU)."
  ]
}